# Frontend conventions

- Plain JavaScript — no TypeScript
- API calls only via `frontend/src/api.js` (never inline `fetch` in components)
- Tailwind for styling; match existing layout and color patterns
- Add `data-testid` on new interactive elements (see `selectors.mdc`)
- Component tests: mock api with `vi.mock('../api')` (or relative path to `api.js`); wrap routed components in `<MemoryRouter>`
